																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">17</div> <div class="vers-content">A thousand men shall flee for fear of one: and for fear of five shall you flee, till you be left as the mast of ship on the top of a mountain, and as an ensign upon a hill.</div></div></td>
